title: Russian Soyuz capsule lands on Earth to return crew of 3 home after months on International Space Station (video)
description: NASA astronaut Jonny Kim and Roscosmos cosmonauts Sergey Ryzhikov and Alexey Zubritsky landed on Russia's Soyuz MS-27  on Dec. 9, 2025, after 245 days on the International Space Station.
content: NASA astronaut Jonny Kim and Roscosmos cosmonauts Sergey Ryzhikov and Alexey Zubritsky landed on Russia's Soyuz MS-27  on Dec. 9, 2025, after 245 days on the International Space Station.
